Citizens can thus seek shelter or prepare buildings for the disaster ahead of time. Prepared buildings suffer less structural damage in the disaster.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[EmergencyShel: More efficient air circulation allows for more people to take shelter here.
Extended stores of rations allow citizens to remain in the shelter for longer.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[LargeEmergencyShelter: A massive shelter that has the space and provisions to house a significant number of citizens for an extended period of time during even the most dangerous of disasters. When an evacuation order is given, specialized buses are sent out from the shelter to collect citizens from the affected areas.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[CityHall01 Co: Increases the effectiveness of the local court system, which in turn brings the crime rate down.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[CityHall01 Pl: Specialized city planners help lower the cost of improving zoned buildings.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[PoliceHeadqua: More cells to hold a larger number of apprehended criminals.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[CentralInvestigationB: The local headquarters for CIB agents. The Central Intelligence Bureau investigates severe criminal activity and apprehends criminals with superior efficiency. The sole existence of the office lowers crime rate citywide.
Assets.SUB_SERVICE_DESCRIPTION[Education: The level of education affects every aspect of citizens' lives from jobs to consumption habits and garbage production. Education services provide schooling for kids, teens and adults alike.

The activities provided by the playground bring increased well-being to citizens.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[InternationalAirport0: A large international hub that allows citizens the ultimate freedom of travel. The integrated train station, taxi stands and a plenitude of tax free services ensure that citizens and tourists alike enjoy their trip. The shapes of this mansion reflect the art of the sculptor who owns it.

The place where a star of the silver screen withdraws to get a break from the busy world outside.
This painter is known the world over, but chooses to live in this city.

The residents of Halo Heights are able to touch the skies. Luxurious homes for those who aim for the top. The grand design improves the mood of passers-by and attracts tourists.
A round, terraced residential building complex that elicits feelings of triumph of both its residents as well as everyone around.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[NA_MixedSignature03]: Bespoke suits and dresses are made in the bottom floor tailor shop, while high-end residences fill the upper floors.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EU_ResidentialMediumR: Citizens will be dizzy with excitement living here!
This beautiful old style building lifts the spirits of everyone passing by.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EU_MixedSignature01]: Luxurious living spaces atop a high-end restaurant. Made for those who appreciate life for its pleasures.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EU_MixedSignature02]: Art and high-end housing go hand in hand in this building. A multi-floored gallery space at the bottom is completed by luxury residences above.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EU_MixedSignature03]: Life is all about fun and games in this residential building that houses a famous toy store on the bottom floor.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[NA_ResidentialMediumS: Residents will enjoy the atmosphere of this smooth, luxurious building.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[NA_ResidentialMediumR: A stone monolith that diversifies and enhances its surroundings.

An exquisitely decorated red brick building that celebrates its developer's first decade in the business and radiates warm and welcoming vibes.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EU_ResidentialMediumS: A modern classic that puts a smile on the faces of its inhabitants.
An old factory converted into luxurious living spaces that spark joy in their inhabitants.
The smooth, arched shapes simply boggle the mind of everyone around. But in a good way.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[NA_ResidentialHighSig: A residential glass-walled monolith that reaches almost impossibly high into the sky.
Old styled luxurious residential skyscraper building with a castle-like construction on top. Lifts peoples' spirits and attracts tourists.
A modern glass and steel skyscraper with a curious, angular design.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Nasinneula]: Näsinneula is an observation tower in Tampere, Finland. Opened in 1971, the tower is located in the Särkänniemi amusement park, overseeing Lake Näsijärvi. A revolving restaurant is located in the top of the tower, with one revolution taking 45 minutes.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[NationalGalleryofArts: A national art museum in Washington, D.C. Established in 1937, the museum is open to the public and free of charge.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[BotanicalGarden01]: A huge greenhouse that displays wondrous plantlife from all over the globe.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[FountainPlaza01]: A massive, round plaza with concentric fountains.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[OldCastle01]: A restored medieval castle open for visitors.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[NotreDame]: Notre-Dame de Paris is the world-famous French medieval Gothic cathedral. Built over the years from 1163 to 1345, it has become one of the most widely recognized symbols of the city of Paris.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[Service Budgets]: City Service budgets can be lowered if needed to save on expenses. However, as less money is directed towards a service, its quality also suffers.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Trade]: Resources and some City Services can be imported and exported as required. Resource trade happens automatically between citizens and companies and the outside world, while City Service trade can be limited by adjusting relevant budgets.

Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[CoalPowerPlan: A more efficient burn process allows the same power output with less fuel.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[WindTurbine01: Upgraded systems allow for a significant increase in power output.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[Heliport01 Me: Improved maintenance facilities for medical helicopters. Allows them to get back into action quicker.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[Heliport01 Po: Improved maintenance facilities for police helicopters. Allows them to get back into action quicker.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[Heliport01 Fi: Improved maintenance facilities for firefighting helicopters. Allows them to get back into action quicker.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[CoalPowerPlant01]:
A power plant that burns coal to produce electricity. Fairly inexpensive to build and maintain, but generates lots of pollution.
Can be upgraded with an additional turbine, enlarged coal storage, exhaust filter and an advanced furnace.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[RoadMaintenanceDepot0:
Base of operations for road maintenance personnel, their tools and vehicles. Road maintenance comprises road repairs, snow clearing, and traffic accident clean-up.
Can be upgraded with an extra garage for a larger maintenance vehicle fleet.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[WindTurbine01]:
Rotating blades combined with a turbine generate power from the wind. Power output is dependent on placement and weather conditions, but wind turbines generate no pollution.
Can be upgraded with a storage battery, solar panels, and an advanced rotor design.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[SewageOutlet01]:
A basic sewage processing facility that pumps waste water out into the environment.
Can be upgraded with an additional settling tank and a chemical purification system.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Large Water Pipe]: Single high capacity pipe for moving fresh water.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Large Sewage Pipe]: Single high capacity pipe for moving sewage.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Combined Large Pipe]: Dual high capacity pipes for moving fresh water and sewage.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[MedicalClinic01]:
Basic healthcare for a small area. Can pick up patients with ambulances. Helps citizens in its service area remain healthier.
Can be upgraded with an ambulance depot and an extension wing.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Crematorium01]:
Cremates the bodies of deceased citizens. The ashes do not take up space in the crematorium.
Can be upgraded with a hearse garage, an additional incinerator, and an expanded refrigerator.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Landfill01]:
Sends out garbage trucks to collect waste from the city and stores it in the designated area.
Can be upgraded with a garbage truck depot, a hazardous waste collection point, and a waste recycling unit.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[IncinerationPlant01]:
Collects and burns garbage, turning it into energy. This reduces garbage accumulation, but produces some air pollution.
Can be upgraded with a garbage truck depot, an extra incinerator, and an extended storage.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[RecyclingCenter01]:
Collects and sorts garbage to produce reusable materials, which are then sold further. This produces income for the city.
Can be upgraded with a garbage truck depot, a hazardous waste collection point, and an extended storage.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Landfill Site Lot]: Adjusts the dumping area of a landfill. A larger area can store more garbage.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[FireHouse01]:
A small station that houses a few fire engines. Also reduces the likelihood of fires in the buildings in its service area by conducting safety supervision.
Can be upraded with an extended garage.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[FireStation01]:
A large station that houses several fire engines. Also reduces the likelihood of fires in the buildings in its service area by conducting safety supervision.
Can be upgraded with an extended garage, a training facility, a disaster response unit, and a helipad that provides firefighting helicopters.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EmergencyShelter01]:
Provides citizens a safe place to stay during large-scale accidents or natural disasters.
Can be upgraded with advanced air recycling and extra stores of consumables.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[PoliceStation01]:
A base of operations for local police. Houses staff facilities, an attached garage for squad cars and a small jail.
Can be upgraded with an extended garage.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[PoliceHeadquarters01]:
A large station house with administrative and staff facilities, a large garage and a jail.
Can be upgraded with an extended garage,  extra jail cells, and a helipad that provides police helicopters.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[ElementarySchool01]:
A place of basic education for children. Provides the first level of education. 
Can be upgraded with an extension wing, a children's clinic, and a playground.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[HighSchool01]:
A school for teenagers. Provides the second level of education. 
Can be upgraded with an extension wing, a sports field, and a library.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[College01]:
The first step towards higher education for teens and adults alike. Provides the third level of education. 
Can be upgraded with an extension wing, and a library.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[University01]:
A massive complex that offers education for academically oriented citizens. Provides the fourth level of education. 
Can be upgraded with an extension wing, a library, and a park.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[BusDepot01]:
Fuels, maintains and stores buses. Each vehicle stops by the depot at certain intervals to stay in running order. 
Can be upgraded with an extra garage and electric buses.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[TaxiDepot01]:
A garage and repair workshop for taxis. Also houses a small dispatch office. 
Can be upgraded with an extra garage, a dispatch center, and electric taxis.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[TrainStation01]:
Allows passengers train boarding and disembarking. 
Can be upgraded with extra platforms, station services, a subway interface and a taxi stop.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[CargoTrainTerminal01]:
A large warehouse where cargo trains can load and unload cargo to and from trucks. 
Can be upgraded with a storage warehouse and extra tracks.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[TramDepot01]:
Workshops and staff facilities for the tram network. Trams return to the depot for maintenance at regular intervals. 
Can be upgraded with an extra garage.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[SubwayStation02]:
Allows passengers subway train boarding and disembarking overground. 
Can be upgraded with station services.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[SubwayYard01]:
Rail yard that contains warehouses and facilities for subway train handling and maintenance. 
Can be upgraded with extra tracks and a maintenance hall.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[Harbor01]:
Passenger ships stop here to load and unload. A passenger terminal allows passengers to board and disembark. 
Can be upgraded with an extra pier and a transit terminal.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[CargoHarbor01]:
A harbor with cranes and container yards that allows for cargo ships to load and unload. Also stores the cargo until it is shipped forward.
Can be upgraded with a railway connection, extra cargo cranes, and warehouses.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[PostOffice01]:
Handles local incoming and outgoing mail. Post vans and trucks pick up mail from mailboxes around the city. Citizens can also drop off their mail directly at the office. 
Can be upgraded with an extra garage and a storage extension.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[PostSortingFacility01:
Processes and stores both local and intercity mail. Mail going to and coming from outside the city is carried by high capacity post trucks, which helps reduce mail related traffic on the roads. 
Can be upgraded with extra loading ramps, a storage extension and automated sorting systems.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[RadioMast01]:
Transmits mobile data, radio traffic and TV signals. In case of emergencies, the masts are used to broadcast an alarm which allows citizens to react to the event more rapidly. 
Can be upgraded with a wireless network antenna and increased bandwidth.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[ServerFarm01]:
Rows and banks of raw computing power provide immense resources to handle network traffic. 
Can be upgraded with fiber optic cables and advanced computers.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[AppleTree01]: Apple trees are deciduous trees often cultivated for their fruit. The trees exist all over the world.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[OakTree01]: Oaks have distinctly shaped leaves and produce acorns. They are native to the Northern Hemisphere.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[BirchTree01]: Birches are thin-leaved, deciduous hardwood trees. They are widespread throughout the Northern Hemisphere.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[PineTree01]: Pines are evergreen, coniferous, resinous trees typically used for lumber. They are native to the Northern Hemisphere.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[SpruceTree01]: Spruces are coniferous, evergreen trees. They typically exist in the northern temperate and boreal regions.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[NA_HickoryTree01]: Hickories are temperate forest trees that produce edible nuts and are often used for lumber. They are native to the Asian and North American continents.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[NA_LondonPlaneTree01]: London planes are a large, deciduous trees with thick leaves. They are a hybrid of the oriental plane and American sycamore.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[NA_LindenTree01]: The lindens are medium-sized to large deciduous trees. They are native to North America.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EU_ChestnutTree01]: Chestnuts are deciduous trees that produce edible nuts. They are native to temperate regions of the Northern Hemisphere.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EU_AlderTree01]: Alders are deciduous trees commonly used in woodworking. They are found mostly in the Northern Hemisphere.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[EU_PoplarTree01]: Poplars are decidious trees often used for paper manufacturing. They are native to the Northern Hemisphere.

Assets.SUB_SERVICE_DESCRIPTION[Healthcar: Keeping citizens in good health helps them live longer and contribute to the day-to-day activities of the city. A lacking healthcare system leads to increased number of sick citizens.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[CentralBank01]: Houses stock and resource traders as well as financial advisors and loan officers. The services working together lowers loan interests and reduces the price of imported resources.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[RadioTelescope01]: An astronomy research facility that increases the citizens' interest in university level education and leads to increased university graduation rates.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[LargeHadronCollider01: A huge particle collider that is used for various physics experiments. Increases citizens' interest in university studies and generates higher demand for electronics and software companies.

Academic learning for the technically oriented. Provides the fourth level of education, and increases the efficiency of offices and industrial companies.
Can be upgraded with an extension wing, and a workshop upgrade.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[XianBellTower]: Originally built in 1384 during the early Ming Dynasty, this brick and timber bell tower is the largest and most well preserved of its kind. It stands as a symbol of ancient China at the center of the city of Xi'an.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[TheNationalDiet]: This building is  where both houses of the Japanese legislature, the National Diet, meet. Located in Tokyo, the building was completed in 1936, and it is constructed almost solely out of Japanese materials.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[SungnyemunGate]: Namdaemun is one of the Eight Gates in the Fortress Wall of Seoul, South Korea, which surrounded the city in 14th century. First built in 1398, and rebuilt in 1447, it is a historic pagoda-style gateway, and is designated as the first National Treasure of South Korea.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[Small Water Pipe]: Single pipe for moving fresh water between parts of the fresh water network.

Delivers fresh water into the city via water pipes. Costly to maintain when compared to its output capacity, but can be placed anywhere. 
Can be upgraded with a viewing deck.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[DiseaseControlCenter0:
A research facility for pathogens, toxins, and hereditary diseases. Citizens afflicted by them are also treated here. Intensive care takes slightly longer than regular treatment, but makes recovery much more likely.

Assets.SUB_SERVICE_DESCRIPTION[RoadsHigh:

Due to high driving speeds, highways generate large amounts of noise pollution, which prohibits zoning around them.

Assets.DESCRIPTION[MuscleCarGarage01]: Cool and special cars sold, bought and repaired right here!
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[SolarPowerSta: Allows for a new Power Line to be built from the plant.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[SolarPowerStation01]:
Photovoltaic cells generate electricity from sunlight. It is stored in batteries during daytime and fed into the network during nights. As power is generated from sunlight alone, power output depends on the weather, but the plant also does not produce any ground or air pollution.
Can be upgraded with a backup battery, an advanced tracking system, and high voltage substations.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[GeothermalPow: Allows for a new Power Line to be built from the plant.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[GeothermalPowerPlant0:
Electricity is generated from heat drawn from deep underground, so no fuel source is needed for these power plants. As a downside, they are somewhat expensive to build and maintain. Some greenhouse gasses also leak into the atmosphere in the process, causing air pollution. 
Can be upgraded with an additional turbine, a more efficient power generation process, and high voltage substations.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[High-voltage Line]: Heavy cables for transferring high voltage currents between power plants and transformer stations.
Assets.DESCRIPTION[TransformerStation01]: Transforms high voltage currents coming from a power plant to low voltage current usable by buildings.
Assets.UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION[GeothermalPow: Allows the plant to use lower geothermal temperatures, which increases power output somewhat.
